Package main.webapp.servlet

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutUsServlet  
    AdministratorServlet
    Administrator Servlet is used to add or remove components and administrators from db
    ApplicationServer  
    ConfigurationServlet
    Servlet used to handle the creation and editing of configurations and show the relative page.
    HomeServlet
    Used to show the home page, containing 3 configurations as a showcase for the project.
    LoginServlet
    Servlet used to handle login, saving user informations through sessions.
    LogoutServlet
    Servlet used to handle logout, removing user informations contained in session.
    MyServlet
    main servlet
    ProfileServlet
    Servlet used to show profile page, containg information about the user, such as his name, and his saved configurations.
    RegisterServlet  
    ServletController
    Class that serves as a link between all servlets and our model.
